<Content>
<Comment><![CDATA[Inicialización del problema]]></Comment>
<Code><![CDATA[
if (dt*dt>dx*dx/(c*c)) 
  _alert ("mainFrame","Warning","dt is too big");
t = 0.0;
// Initial condition given by f
for (int i=0, n=m+1; i<=n; i++) u0[i] = _view.function.evaluate(x[i]);

]]></Code>

